-- Formosa Plastics May Boost Ningbo Investment by $700 Million, Daily Says
-- Yu-Huay Sun
-- 2010-06-24T23:21:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/formosa-plastics-may-boost-ningbo-investment-by-700-million-daily-says.html

          
          
             Formosa Plastics Corp.’s board will 
discuss in August a proposal to increase the company’s 
investment in China’s Ningbo city by $700 million, the Apple 
Daily reported, without saying where it got the information.  
          
          


  


        